lass=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"o\">},</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Icc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>(with a pedestrian proof through <code>IccExtend</code> and unfolding the compact-open topology).</p>",
